  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Grow Crops</strong></h2>As you grow more crops, more will become available to you!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Raise livestock</strong></h2>Take care of cows, chickens, sheep, and more to make money on your mission to save the once bustling town of Layala!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Make Friends</strong></h2>Meet interesting people around town and develop relationships with them to learn about the area!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Go Fishing</strong></h2>Catch a variety of fish in the waters around Layala!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Get Achievements</strong></h2>As you explore and discover the ways of farming, you'll find a number of Steam Exclusive Achievements for doing so!<br><br><br>Excitement awaits in this one of a kind Farming RPG!",
